  <title>GLib.ThreadPool.stop_unused_threads</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function stop_unused_threads(): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_thread_pool_stop_unused_threads()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Stops all currently unused threads. This does not change the
maximal number of unused threads. This function can be used to
regularly stop all unused threads e.g. from <link xref="GLib.timeout_add"/>.</p>


